Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.48,sign_0_1_Tatara_Nishi_Hig,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tatara Nishi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:04.78,Main,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki Mari-san and Kobuchizawa \NShirase-san will be embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.70,Main,vo,0000,0000,0000,,on a trip to Antarctica next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:07.48,Main,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.83,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a little hard to \Nbelieve this is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:16.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll do my best where I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:20.79,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.60,Flashback,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have waited so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.39,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.06,Flashback,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.89,Italics,meg,0000,0000,0000,,It made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.09,Flashback,mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're very smart, Megumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:01.70,Italics,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I had become a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:03.33,Flashback,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.41,Flashback,meg,0000,0000,0000,,We can play together tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:43.51,Likes/Comments,title,0000,0000,0000,,1 Like\N1 Comment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:43.51,Hashtags,title,0000,0000,0000,,#100kgAllTogether  #GirlsTea #TheMadness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.10,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the new Antarctic Icebreaker ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,modified from the {\i1}Shirase II{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.81,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,the Shichishinya {\i1}Penguin Manju{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Its basic performance hasn't changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.99,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,but there have been some \Ninternal modifications,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.92,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,and as you can see, it's had \Na big external makeover!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.72,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go inside!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.04,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I'd like to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:08.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is, we won't get to \Nboard it until we reach Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.31,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's make the jump \Nto Australia right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.53,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.45,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That's a wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.52,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What a total pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.01,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're not! We're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We genuinely respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:30.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,By comparison, our next report's \Nnot until we reach Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,but look at her freaking out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:35.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm here in Autsralia. Wait! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.36,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I have to jump first...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.40,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,then land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.57,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Land, then jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:41.68,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Land means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.66,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-san, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.69,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?! \NI can't land in Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.30,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,They can work it out in editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.21,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just do your vocal warm-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing your warm-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She sells seashells on the sea floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.05,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite right, but close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a person sell seashells?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.55,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't try to dissect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She spoke just fine at morning assembly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no one she \Nsees as an enemy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When someone she's hostile \Nto is around, it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:15.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,the "screw you!" switch gets flipped "on."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You! You're talking about me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.09,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We're really getting on this thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished packing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. There's a lot to \Nthink about, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:38.78,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Including our body weight, \Nwe're allowed 100 kilograms all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It should be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we're staying \Nfor three months, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.41,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's over 90 changes of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Do laundry occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:52.94,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a journey, once we arrive, \Nwe'll just be living life like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.15,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,And there'll be lots of work to do, \Nso they say it'll pass quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.65,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But when you start thinking and \Npacking things into the boxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.65,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,it does end up being quite a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.18,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you not even gotten started?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.54,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But it just needs to be less than \N100 kilograms, including body weight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,For me, that's 50, 52, 53...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I can take upwards of \N58 kilograms of luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.92,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Underestimating your weight \Nis a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-eight kilograms? \NThat means you weigh 42 kilograms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave my arm flab alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This might be harder than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:44.04,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-chan, how many times do I have to \Ntell you to carry up your own laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.07,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.29,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.41,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll need cooking supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:00.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You think? It's diamond-coated! \NNothing sticks to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:02.60,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,An inner tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.50,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,An English-Japanese dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.80,sign_8762_97_Junior_Ace_Engli,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Junior Ace\N{\c&H38373A&}English-Japanese Dictionary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:12.18,sign_8768_98_Junior_Ace_Japan,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Junior Ace\N{\c&H29332C&}Japanese-English Dictionary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:06.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese-English dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.80,sign_8792_101_Conversational_E,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Conversational English\Nfor Travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Conversational English for Travel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:08.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A peeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Conversational Chinese for Travel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:12.18,sign_8843_104_Conversational_C,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Conversational Chinese\Nfor Travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Reliable World Travel Guide{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.18,sign_8885_105_The_Reliable_Wor,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Reliable\N{\c&H54D0CF&}World Travel Guide
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I bought them all just for this trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.29,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be with tons of people \Nwho can speak foreign languages!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.56,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So little!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.96,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,You should consult with Shirase-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.60,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some specific \Nthings you'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think this'll be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be gone for over three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.47,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis... are you sure you can handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.33,sign_9521_118_Comprehensive_Su,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Comprehensive\NSummer Training Documents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:41.79,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that pamphlets \Ntell us what to bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.09,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's an adult thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.71,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Responsible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Adulting is hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.14,sign_9936_124_Pen_Pen,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pen-Pen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.64,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.90,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.42,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:09.72,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's your game! \NThe one I thought I'd lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.70,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd totally forgotten about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.80,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You don't actually have to test it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.41,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't seen it in so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.31,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,After three years, it might not even work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.76,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You sure loved this thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:39.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's the only \Ngame I ever beat you at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:40.98,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't beat me at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,so you said you'd lend it to \Nme as long as I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.32,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.32,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.61,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,But I did beat it before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.12,sign_11398_146_Yay_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.12,sign_11398_147_I_lose_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I lose~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.19,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.14,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd things go in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty well, for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.19,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Did Antarctica manage to \Nget through her report?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica? Oh, Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan doesn't have \Nto report for a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.30,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty weird, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:17.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:21.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She swings between super-confident \Nand super-timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to Hinata-chan about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.39,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the girl from your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.19,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.85,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuzuki-chan did the \Nreport perfectly, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.45,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the girl from Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.07,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.92,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.58,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, you'll just \Nregret it all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.83,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.29,Flashback,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.51,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.20,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.01,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge for Antarctic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.99,sign_13365_171_A_Place_Further_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Place Further Than\N{\c&H99A591&}the Universe\NKobuchizawa Takako
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.72,sign_13834_172_Yuri_chan,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.05,sign_13853_173_Aina,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Aina
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.30,sign_13884_174_Delete,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Delete
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.99,sign_14182_176_Challenge_for_An,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge for Antarctic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:02.49,sign_0_1_Tatara_Nishi_Hig,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tatara Nishi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.75,sign_14467_178_Good_luck_in_Ant,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Good {\c&H769981&}luck {\c&H6E8C73&}in {\c&H597A5E&}Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.75,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.35,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me an iceberg, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure it'll fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.82,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you pictures of warm things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.69,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does your snot freeze in Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.38,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna have some shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.75,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true there's a UFO \Nburied in the ice there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like I'm changing \Nschools or something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, pudding shakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be seeing you for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.65,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of reception did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't think they'd \Nmake such a big deal over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When Shirase-chan said she \Nwas going to Antarctica,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,everyone just made fun of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.76,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Because they didn't think \Nshe'd make it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.11,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, some people still make fun of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.42,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.76,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to come here \Nfor three months, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.51,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.97,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.89,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I just wasn't sure how I'd feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:13.58,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe it's best \Nnot to show off so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:17.03,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people think you're \Ngetting full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not showing off anything. \NI'm leaving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.35,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.08,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, they're saying \Nsome awful things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.93,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Out of jealousy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:33.05,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,That you shoplifted from convenience \Nstores to raise money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.09,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,That you were messing around with \Nboys in Kabukicho and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.59,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.59,sign_16726_211_Girls__Strawberr,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(190,1)}Girls'\NStrawberry Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:42.09,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, people think \Nyou're full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:44.86,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:45.83,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:49.37,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should just \Nleave with this unresolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.10,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're back, \Nit's only going to get worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.11,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Would this be Megu-chan, by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:00.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you guys haven't met yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:07.07,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyake Hinata, Kimari's co-worker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:07.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.78,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:09.92,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:10.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.37,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff you said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Who's saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.08,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I just heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'll search out the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.46,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, we're heading out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.64,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit back while someone \Nspreads those ridiculous rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:30.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Starting a fight now won't help anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.43,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You've ignored all the \Nnasty rumors so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,These are bald-faced lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.69,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,To claim we've been messing \Naround with boys in Shinjuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.54,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We did go to Shinjuku, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:42.70,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But we weren't messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.66,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Can you prove that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.29,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, people are just mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight mean with mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.79,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.01,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a quote?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're not alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you have people to vent with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.14,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:13.14,sign_18921_256_Rest_Station,sign,0000,0000,0000,,R{\c&HAACCFB&}est {\c&H696DC7&}Stat{\c&HACCCEF&}i{\c&H6D69B4&}on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:13.14,sign_18921_257_Udon___Soba,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Udon   Soba
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.91,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.85,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This must be what it feels to grab \Na drink on the way back from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it might.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.52,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's have one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's payday, so the old man'll cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.80,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's extremely exasperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You sure hate to let things go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:35.62,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the people spreading the \Nrumors are the ones in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I yield to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.78,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to scream at the top of my lungs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Scream, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.63,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Next to a temple? Not a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go to karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.64,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,If we do it within the hour, \Nwe're probably good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.85,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.70,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How can you all do something so embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to get it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's our going-away party!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.15,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're invited, too, Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.47,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}invited{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.95,sign_20346_287_Karaoke_Parlor_T,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke Parlor\N{\fs18\c&HF3CEBF&}Tanuki-Neko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's raise the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:16.94,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Takahashi Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.46,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,My friend, Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.88,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Let's raise the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:50.49,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H606ACB&\b1\bord2\shad0\an8\3c&H294888&}The {\c&H6CD6B4&}Madness {\c&HCAD6AA&}of {\c&H39D9E7&}Shi{\c&HCA84D1&}rase
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.19,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so refreshed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.00,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tonight's been the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd get to do this \Nstuff the night before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:06.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I haven't gotten \Nto hang out with you much
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,since I decided to go to Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:11.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess that was a relief to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.01,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.02,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:17.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't like that for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,About how I want to go far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,about how I hate being where I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,about how I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew why I felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably because of you, Megu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:39.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always uncertain, \Nneeding you to fuss over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Always clinging to you, \Nasking what I should do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.50,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.25,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I always hated that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I think I wanted to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:54.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn't just be clinging to you; \NI wouldn't be worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be someone you could \Nplay video games with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna do my best out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what's all this? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.83,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.95,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,A special treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:22.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.33,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, there's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Egg Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.84,sign_23793_335_Come_and_eat_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Come and eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.33,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:15.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later. See you later. \NSee you later. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.80,sign_24847_339_I_m_in,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:20.81,sign_24860_340_I_m_out,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:22.81,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.18,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get breakfast in Tokyo, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:26.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.46,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:32.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.23,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.95,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll keep myself safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:07.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.93,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you right before you set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:11.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.73,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,I came to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.99,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, we're not friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.18,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:32.30,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think the rumor about you and \NAntarctica going to Shinjuku came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.00,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell anyone about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.21,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.98,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,The first time you met Antarctica,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.42,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,how did those older girls \Nknow she had a million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:46.72,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,How did your mother know you were going \Nto Antarctica before you told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.77,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Because I told them, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:58.69,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd finally catch \Non and get mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.07,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:00.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:06.03,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,But you and Antarctica and the others \Nare such morons you didn't catch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:06.95,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.96,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.59,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I got so \Nmad when you first told me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.39,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,you were going to Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:22.23,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You always consulted with me \Nbefore you did anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.72,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.49,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've put you through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.23,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.63,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:35.19,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when you were \Ntalking, I finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:39.99,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the one hanging on, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.92,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Having you rely on me, consult with \Nme... me getting exasperated with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.54,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,pretending to mother you, \Nacting so smart around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:55.50,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I didn't have that, \NI didn't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:02.80,sign_28695_387_Civilian_Icebrea,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Civilian Icebreaker Ship Leaves \NPort for First Time in Three Years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:20:02.24,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,And because I wasn't anything, \NI didn't want you to have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.31,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one who was worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.14,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.56,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who needs to go \Nsomewhere that isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.30,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.33,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:38.56,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.09,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,To Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.29,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.26,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally taking my first step
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.66,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,into a world without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.15,sign_30255_399_New_Message,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.15,sign_30255_400_To__Mom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,To: {\c&H545554&}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.86,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking our first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:11.06,Italics,shira,0000,0000,0000,,To a world without any of the \Nthings we usually rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.87,Italics,hina,0000,0000,0000,,To a world where we don't know \Nwhat lies around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:18.38,Italics,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where we don't even know which way home is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:23.69,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,To a world where we don't \Nknow where we'll be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.88,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Where we can't even imagine where \Nwe'll be headed the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yet we're taking that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.35,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Breakup rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.66,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Water collects into stagnant pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:41.14,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved watching \Nit spill out all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.99,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking free, liberated, rushing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.35,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The energy stored up during \Nits stagnation bursts forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:53.50,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Everything springs into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:03.01,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Everything springs into action!
